title: Giant-Size Mini Comics (Eclipse)
description:
The Eclipse Comics Upload Project steams ahead like poop thru a goose, with 'Giant-Size Mini Comics'!

GSMC was a four-issue series published in 1986 and 1987 which featured work by artists and writers who self-published. Each issue was edited by a different person who was well-known in the mini-comics world. Creators include Larry Marder, Erik Larson and... and... well, a bunch of people you've likely never heard of. Still, some interesting stuff and a nice window into the times.

All four issues are contained within. Thank you scanners! Thank you creators that I don't really recognize! Get it, seed it!
